Class MapBasedJobFactory

java.lang.Object
net.greghaines.jesque.worker.MapBasedJobFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
JobFactory
public class MapBasedJobFactory extends Object implements JobFactory
MapBasedJobFactory uses a map of job names and types to materialize jobs.
